    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## オプション"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "061veB7IsP6MLX2VaAsyznYrdLIx3av88lknlRwMrww=",
    "originContent": "## Options",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### pages"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "k8KUALzXZYrNdwJvZIi+98KHgi3FusZa5LNPloIbIl8=",
    "originContent": "### pages",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "事前レンダリングされたページを書き出すディレクトリ。デフォルトは `build` です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "a+GTQBv5QTA88Qw9vjo0h6it/Wrx5kw04KWdpstxl0k=",
    "originContent": "The directory to write prerendered pages to. It defaults to `build`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### assets"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "V5EVeSC0jb20WQQHblY6Xh+I7s5662Z7VZXt1+8bufo=",
    "originContent": "### assets",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "静的アセットを書き出すディレクトリ（`static` の内容に加え、SvelteKit によって生成されたクライアントサイドのJSおよびCSS）。通常は `pages` と同じにすべきで、デフォルトも `pages` の値に従いますが、稀にページとアセットを別々の場所に出力する必要がある場合があります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "uqqwRyKdgD0Vya7HRkCbepXySzsEa62TeBZS4F/f1Eo=",
    "originContent": "The directory to write static assets (the contents of `static`, plus client-side JS and CSS generated by SvelteKit) to. Ordinarily this should be the same as `pages`, and it will default to whatever the value of `pages` is, but in rare circumstances you might need to output pages and assets to separate locations.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### fallback"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "WEFc+ItFoHBA48YbmCPEOd2kjnq8dQBErXENjZ0mN6I=",
    "originContent": "### fallback",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "SPAモードのフォールバックページを指定します。例えば `index.html` や `200.html`、`404.html` など。"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "qT2GxSu9t71kiO1KFphiUg1BGUmnyJTIIiCh3F+raHM=",
    "originContent": "Specify a fallback page for SPA mode, e.g. `index.html` or `200.html` or `404.html`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### precompress"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "Ps44qpJ341rqTjP+pRhVNPISQks68ljiSk1QRhaHbYw=",
    "originContent": "### precompress",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`true` の場合、ファイルをbrotliおよびgzipで事前圧縮します。これにより `.br` と `.gz` ファイルが生成されます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "xZYtIMz8mslSHt9dfc+qylsCKcWD5omIEIvf2szWSV0=",
    "originContent": "If `true`, precompresses files with brotli and gzip. This will generate `.br` and `.gz` files.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### manifest"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "aNS9+y4FmJPnf1/DFmwL7xMd0/JGUp74bk4655Zkbyg=",
    "originContent": "### manifest",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "異なるターゲットプラットフォーム用に異なるマニフェストを使用したい場合に、マニフェストファイル名を指定します。例：`chrome_manifest.json`、`firefox_manifest.json`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "6nn0eq2bFjU+EcuHCtIWlwHEHZiUOIWk1En2Iri+y7o=",
    "originContent": "Specify manifest file name if you want different manifests for different target platforms, e.g. `chrome_manifest.json`, `firefox_manifest.json`.",
    "translatedContent": "このファイル名は `static` ディレクトリ（静的ファイルを含むディレクトリ）に存在する必要があります。選択されたターゲットファイルはビルドディレクトリで `manifest.json` にリネームされ、その他の `manifest` を含む `.json` ファイルはコピーされません。"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "j/KHAzHBVLRFJ6TGeLWKgd2XbyHonuHR2ciUo/V+0fk=",
    "originContent": "This file name must match one that is present in the `static` directory (the dir containing your static files). The selected target file will be renamed to `manifest.json` in the build directory, and all other `.json` files with `manifest` in the name won't be copied.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
